下许多产品，都是运行在我们电脑上，最庞大的就是Adobe flash player（这是浏览器播放视频，flash必不可少的插件!）\r\n还有就是PhotoShop，AfterEffect等图像，视频处理软件，高效简洁的操作方式，花式各异的功能。\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/4572067_152904392391_2.jpg\"><img src=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/4572067_152904392391_2.jpg\" alt=\"4572067_152904392391_2\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-294\" /></a>\r\n[dm href=\'http://www.adobe.com/\']Adobe官网[/dm]\r\n\r\n<h2>如何安装呢？</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>1、首先注册Adobe账号<a href=\"http://www.adobe.com/\" target=\"_blank\">官网注册</a></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>2、下载Adobe Creative Cloud安装包与破解文件</h3>\r\n[dl href=\'http://pan.baidu.com/s/1hqm5Bla/\']百度网盘[/dl]\r\n\r\n<h3>3、安装CreativeCloudSet-Up.exe文件，并打开登入</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>4、选择Photoshop CC 2015进行下载安装</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/1.png\"><img src=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/1.png\" alt=\"1\" width=\"446\" height=\"787\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-295\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<h3>5、打开PS可以看到30天的试用期</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>6、关闭PS打开破解文件adobe.exe</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>7、选择最新的PS就行</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/2.png\"><img src=\"http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/2.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"441\" height=\"324\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-296\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<h3>8、点击Patch会弹出一个Not found!(原因是文件夹找不到，要自己查找)</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>9、点击是！ 定位到PS所在文件夹下的amtlib.dll选择替换。</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>10、破解完成</h3>\r\n\r\n','如何安装Adobe系列软件（Ps,Ae,Pr,Ai,Dw...etc）','','publish','open','open','','%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85adobe%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%ef%bc%88psaepraidw-etc%ef%bc%89','','','2015-11-27 21:10:02','2015-11-27 13:10:02','',0,'http://blog.limonplayer.cn/?p=287',0,'post','',0),(288,1,'2015-11-27 20:54:41','2015-11-27 12:54:41','','789','','inherit','open','closed','','789','','','2015-11-27 20:54:41','2015-11-27 12:54:41','',287,'http://blog.limonplayer.cn/wp-content/up